strings.Value: "I'll manage anyway. Nok-Nok is a Hero, Nok-Nok can!"
"I am fine. Don't worry. Nok-Nok will protect you anyway."
"Just look at this gnat! Barely alive and still tries to be a hero! Ha!"
"That's the spirit! Even goblins are braver than some southern warriors!"
"I can't afford you to get hurt because of your boldness. So try to keep behind our backs until you feel better, please."
"I would be able to make an entertaining little zombie when this creature perishes. I doubt we'll need to wait long."
